<p>How can you possibly say that the penalties for impaired driving are too harsh.  I have been charged myself and have acceptet responsibility for whatever the costs have been.  We chose to get behind the wheel of our car after drinking and the potential for killing some poor innocent person because of a stupid choice is huge.<br />
You need to take ownership of your decision and stop blaming other people for your choices!<br />
In my opinion the punishment for DUI are not harsh enough.<br />
Think about it and take responsibility for your iinappropriate choice.</p>
